<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.226847>
    dc:description "FIGURE 8. Cylindroiulus oromii n. sp. habitus of adult female in situ and preserved. Scale bar: 2 mm. (Inset: photo of live specimen, courtesy of É. Nunes)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/226847/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.226848>
    dc:description "FIGURES 9 – 14. Cylindroiulus oromii n. sp. male gonopod. 9 – 10: mesal view, 11: pro- & mesomerite, anterior view, 12 – 13: lateral view, 14: opisthomerite, posterior view. afl: anterior flagellum-conducting lamella, f: flagellum, fl: flagelliferous lobe of promerite, fp: finger-shaped projection of promerite, m: mesomerite, p: promerite, pc: lateral rim of paracoxite, pfl: posterior flagellum-conducting lamella, pp: paracoxal process, s: solenomerite, sc: sperm channel, t: apical fringe. Scale bar: 100 µm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/226848/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.226849>
    dc:description "FIGURE 15. Cylindroiulus oromii n. sp. vulva. bu: bursa, op: operculum, rs: receptaculum seminis,. Scale bar: 100 µm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/226849/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

